<div id="home" class="content-section">
    <h2>Home/Landing Page</h2>
    <p>The Home page is your dashboard where you can quickly access recent meetings, upcoming events, and important notices. It provides an overview of the meeting management system.</p>
    <img src="images/home.jpg" alt="Home Page Screenshot">
</div>

<div id="create" class="content-section">
    <h2>Create Meeting</h2>
    <p>On the Create Meeting page, you can schedule new meetings. Fill in the meeting details such as title, date, and type. You can also select items from previous meetings to carry over.</p>
    <img src="images/create.jpg" alt="Create Meeting Page Screenshot">
</div>

<div id="meetings" class="content-section">
    <h2>Meetings</h2>
    <p>The Meetings page lists all scheduled meetings. You can view details, edit meeting information, and manage participants.</p>
    <img src="images/meetings.jpg" alt="Meetings Page Screenshot">
</div>

<div id="meeting-minutes" class="content-section">
    <h2>Meeting Minutes</h2>
    <p>The Meeting Minutes page allows you to record the discussions and decisions made during the meeting. It helps in keeping an official record for future reference.</p>
    <img src="images/meeting-minutes.jpg" alt="Meeting Minutes Page Screenshot">
</div>

<div id="update-status" class="content-section">
    <h2>Update Status</h2>
    <p>On the Update Status page, you can change the status of meeting items. This helps in tracking the progress of tasks and actions decided during the meetings.</p>
    <img src="images/update-status.jpg" alt="Update Status Page Screenshot">
</div>

